39 "§ 53-244.109. Mortgage broker and mortgage lender duties.
40 Any mortgage broker or mortgage lender engaged in the mortgage business as defined by
41 G.S. 53-244.030(11)a., G.S. 53-244.030(11)a. or b., in addition to duties imposed by other
